In [182]:
def outcome_group(x):
    if x == 'Hospitalisation and Discharge well':
        return 'discharge'
    elif x == 'Hospitalisation and Transfer':
        return 'transher'
    elif x == 'Death during hospitalisation':
        return 'death'
    elif x == 'Hospitalisation and Discharge against advice':
        return 'dama'
    elif x == 'Death before admission':
        return 'bid'
    else:
        return 'abscond'
    
df['outcome_group'] = df['Seperation Type'].apply(outcome_group)

def outcome_group(x):
    if x == 'Hospitalisation and Discharge well':
        return 'discharge'
    elif x == 'Hospitalisation and Transfer':
        return 'transher'
    elif x == 'Death during hospitalisation':
        return 'death'
    elif x == 'Hospitalisation and Discharge against advice':
        return 'dama'
    elif x == 'Death before admission':
        return 'bid'
    else:
        return 'abscond'
    
df['outcome_group'] = df['Seperation Type'].apply(outcome_group)
